latestIgtvVideos.title: I made a Short film during a Natural Calamity
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I filmed and edited this video on the night of the storm when electricity was out. At this point, with the natural calamity and the virus, anything outside home(which I'm blessed to have) is dangerous, so here's an overly dramatic 1minute film depicting the same. (It kinda turned out funny but I really like it) I've decided to call it "When the Sky Is Red" or "Apocalypse Outside", where you step out, only to be terrified. 
I am really thankful for whatever I have. The storm has done a world of bad to several people here. I am luckily safe and doing well. So grateful for all those people working hard, in order to restore life and property.
#amphan #prayforbengal #prayfororissa
